      • onPreProcessRequest

        public void onPreProcessRequest(AsyncHttpRequest request)
        This method is called once by the system when the request is about to be processed by the system. The library makes sure that a single request is pre-processed only once. Please note: pre-processing does NOT run on the main thread, and thus any UI activities that you must perform should be properly dispatched to the app's UI thread.
        参数:
        request - The request to pre-process

      • onPostProcessRequest

        public void onPostProcessRequest(AsyncHttpRequest request)
        This method is called once by the system when the request has been fully sent, handled and finished. The library makes sure that a single request is post-processed only once. Please note: post-processing does NOT run on the main thread, and thus any UI activities that you must perform should be properly dispatched to the app's UI thread.
        参数:
        request - The request to post-process
